            <p>
                The main goal of the Internship Management System (InMS) is to manage and monitor the Internship’s student for students in University Malaysia Pahang during their internship duration efficiently.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 footer_grid">
            <h3>Latest News</h3>
            <ul class="footer_grid_list">
                <li>
                    <i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
